      "details": "\n            \n        <div class=\"card-detail-body\">\n            <div class=\"row hmr-6\">\n                <div class=\"col-12 mt-2\">\n                    <h2 class=\"jobtitle mb-1 pb-1\">Matriculants Skills Development and Training (Learnership)</h2>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"row\">\n                <div class=\"col\">\n                    <h2 class=\"opportunity-company mb-1 pb-1\">KE MARKETING</h2>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n                <div class=\"row verified mb-3 mt-0\">\n                    <div class=\"col\">\n                        <p class=\"verified-text\"><i class=\"icon icon-check2-circle\" style=\"margin-right:2px;\"></i><span>Partner Opportunity</span></p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            <div class=\"row\">\n                <div class=\"col\">\n                    <div class=\"card-detail-meta mt-0\">\n                            <div class=\"meta-item\">\n                                <i class=\"icon icon-geo-pin-solid\"></i>\n                                <p class=\"mb-0\"><strong>Location: </strong>Rustenburg, North West</p>\n                            </div>\n\n                            <div class=\"meta-item\">\n                                <i class=\"icon icon-calendar-event-solid\"></i>\n                                <p class=\"mb-0\"><strong>Date posted:</strong> 06 November 2023</p>\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"meta-item\">\n                                <i class=\"icon icon-calendar-x\"></i>\n                                <p class=\"mb-0\"><strong>Closing date:</strong> 24 November 2023 </p>\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"meta-item\">\n                                <i class=\"icon icon-briefcase\"></i>\n                                <p class=\"mb-0\"><strong>Job type: </strong>Full-time / permanent</p>\n                            </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"row\">\n                <div class=\"col\">\n                    <h6 class=\"opportunity-reference mb-3 mt-3\">Reference number: 1224684</h6>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"card-detail-body\">\n            <div class=\"row\">\n                <div class=\"col text-break\">\n                            <h2>Role description</h2>\n                            <p class=\"text-break white-space-pre-line\"></p><p><strong>We Are Hiring for Inbound Consultant for</strong>:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Entry-Level Positions.</li>\n<li>Store-Based Work.</li>\n<li>ASAP Start Dates.</li>\n<li>Full-Time Hours.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Join our team at <strong>KE MARKETING</strong> as a Customer Service Representative and enjoy a fun work environment, ongoing training, above-average compensation, and a range of additional benefits!</p>\n<p><strong>&nbsp;Job Summary:</strong></p>\n<p>This quarter is shaping up to be a busy time of year for our events team. As sales demands grow from our clients we are looking for dedicated individuals to join our Store-based sales team as Customer Service Representatives.</p>\n<p><strong>With training, you will be able to confidently work with our customer base to</strong>:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Provide a great and memorable customer experience.</li>\n<li>Increase customer flow and attract new customers to our event.</li>\n<li>Offer our clients’ products and services to our customers.<br>Answer specific questions and relate to common concerns.</li>\n<li>Record sales transactions and customer information as needed.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br>&nbsp;Rapid advancement opportunities are also going to be available to those who show leadership abilities and have a desire to grow with our start-up! Whether you're looking for a place to build a career in Customer Service or just a part-time job to gain some experience.</p>\n<p><br><strong>Recommended Skills</strong><br>. Customer Experience.<br>. Customer Focussed.<br>. Customer Insight.<br>. Customer Retention.<br>. Customer Service.<br>. Customer Support.</p><p></p>\n                            <h2>Role requirement</h2>\n                            <p class=\"text-break white-space-pre-line\"></p><p>Required Skills and Qualifications:</p>\n<p>Excellent communication skills and the ability to interact with a wide range of people (ie: the general public) Multi-lingual applicants are always encouraged!<br>Customer service skills are essential though they don’t have to be linked to any specific customer-oriented work experience.<br>Confidence in your ability to sell is also important, but the sales we generate are “soft” sales based on conversations not strong-arming people into buying.<br>The ability to work independently and manage personal targets with little or no supervision.<br>Driven to achieve personal and professional goals with the work ethic to match.<br>The ability to think on your feet, solve problems and overcome challenges.<br>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Are 18+ years of age.</li>\n<li>Can stand for long periods of time and work with customers face-to-face.</li>\n<li>Can work flexible hours and days, including some weekends.</li>\n<li>Are able to commute to/from our office in Pretoria.</li>\n<li>Matric/ equivalent.</li>\n</ul><p></p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <hr>\n                                \n        </div>\n    ",
